<p>Family portrait: The U.G.L.Y rapper and the 41-year-old singer - who began dating in December 2006 - are also proud parents of 12-year-old daughter Harlow (posted on May 10) </p>

<p>Thanks, hon! Joel's management company, MDDN, released Richie's 13-track debut comedy rap album Unearthed on August 28 under the alias Nikki Fre$h</p>

<p>On August 30, Nicole hit the red carpet for the first time since COVID-19 thanks to PPE precautions taken by her make-up artist Mai Quynh and hairstylist Davy Newkirk.</p>

<p>The Bless this Mess actress slipped her slim 5ft1in frame into a green Nguyen Cong Tri bubble dress selected by her stylist Jamie Mizrahi.</p>

<p>Richie flew to Manhattan to present the best pop trophy to K-pop boyband BTS and the best R&amp;B trophy to Canadian crooner The Weeknd at the 37th Annual MTV Video Music Awards.</p>

